<br><br></p><div align="center"><img src="http://ti2.auctiva.com/tia/5B6E6/toysonblue/ship.gif"></div><br>We pride ourselves in getting your order to you quickly. (See our feedback to see what our customers say about this) The Shipping charge includes an amount to cover our handling and packaging materials and all costs incurred in making your order available for dispatch as well as the carriers cost of shipping (and where applicable, insurance) for your item(s).<p>
