<b>Payment: If you live outside the UK please note we only accept instant payment methods such as PayPal. </b></p><p>Please make sure your correct postal address is recorded at eBay / PayPal as we use this address when sending your items. Have you moved recently and forgotten to update eBay / PayPal of the new address? </p><p>
